<!--
  Cosmos Footer — canonical unified footer
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  Vendored to all 7 sibling sites for cross-planet brand consistency.
  Source: derived from Earth's layouts/partials/footer.html (9 May 2026 EVE).

  Render target: paste into each sibling's layout. The CSS lives at
  /cosmos-footer.css (vendored alongside).

  All cross-site links are ABSOLUTE (https://www.aguidetocloud.com/...) so
  visitors on shift.aguidetocloud.com / claw.aguidetocloud.com / etc. land
  on the right Earth page when they click feedback / privacy / All Links.

  Year is hardcoded 2026 — bump annually or templatize per-repo.

  Inline SVGs (Lucide-style 14×14 stroke=1.5) avoid the per-repo icon partial
  dependency and keep the footer self-contained.
-->
